data.name: richTextBox2.Text
data.value:
Specify your Project Manager API key or create a new DQF account: https://evaluate.taus.net/
If you already have a DQF account, then you can recover your Project Manager API key by logging into the DQF platform from https://dqf.taus.net/ and click on your user name located at the top right part of the screen to display your account information.

data.name: label50.Text
data.value:
If you do not have a Translator API key, then you can generate one using your own user name && e-mail, simply by clicking on the link 'Request API Translator Key'.
Once created, you will receive an e-mail with the Translator API Key from TAUS; copy and paste that key here.
